{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Do not roll out digital IDs",
        "additional_details": "The government already dropped its mandatory right to work requirement for digital IDs, however we wish to avoid all doubt and stop this being introducing though the back door. We require the government to completely scrap this idea. Do not spend our money on this idea that the public clearly do not agree with.",
        "background": "We do not want digital IDs. We are concerned about total control by the government. Do not spend our money on this system!",
